Pension Funds Management
Institutional investors turn to Herndon Capital Management for a specialized approach to large capitalization equity strategies.
 
Herndon Capital Management is set apart by its research, performance, and the caliber of institutional client relationships they maintain. 
 
Read more...



Large Cap Focus
Herndon Capital’s strategies are rooted in fundamental, bottom-up research of large-cap companies. Our portfolio managers are well-equipped to recognize subtleties often overlooked by other investment professionals.
 
For investors pursuing broader access across the capitalization spectrum, Herndon offers a strategy designed to complement the large caps. Our Mid Cap Value portfolio utilizes the same investment philosophy and processes that have made our large cap value portfolio successful.
Read More...
